  09 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> +metadata.xml:
  Add metadata.xml(s) for QA.

  09 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> source-han-sans-1.004.ebuild:
  Update ebuild file format from "# $Header: $" to "# $Id"

   Since Gentoo changes the VCS from CVS to git, ebuild header is changed.

  20 Jun 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> source-han-sans-1.004.ebuild:
  media-fonts/{noto*,source-han-sans*}: Modify ${DOCs} to list from array.

    font.eclass supports space-delimited listed ${DOCS} only,
   though EAPI(>=4) can treat arrayed ${DOCS}.
    Therefore, space-delimited list (not array) makes codes shorter,
   because src_install can be left as default spec of font.eclass.

  20 Jun 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> source-han-sans-1.004.ebuild:
  dodoc by for-loop.

  20 Jun 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> source-han-sans-1.004.ebuild:
  Trivial code tidy up.

*source-han-sans-1.004 (20 Jun 2015)

  20 Jun 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> -source-han-sans-1.002r.ebuild,
  +source-han-sans-1.004.ebuild:
  Add version 1.004, delete old 1.002r.

  12 May 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> source-han-sans-1.002r.ebuild:
  Declare ${MY_PN} instead of raw string.

*source-han-sans-1.002r (12 May 2015)

